SELECT COUNT(*) as `count`, SUM(`hocphan`.`sotinchi`) as `sum` FROM `hocphan`, `diem` WHERE `diem`.`idhocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `diem`.`idsinhvien`='170040014';
SELECT COUNT(*) as `count`, SUM(`hocphan`.`sotinchi`) as `sum` FROM `hocphan`, `diem` WHERE `diem`.`idhocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `diem`.`diem` < 1 AND `diem`.`idsinhvien`='170040014';
SELECT `diem`, `hocphan`.`tenhocphan`, `hocphan`.`sotinchi` FROM `diem`, `hocphan` WHERE `diem`.`idhocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `diem`.`idsinhvien` = '170040014';

SELECT `idcaytientrinh`, `tencaytientrinh`, `tenkhoa` FROM `caytientrinh` WHERE 1
SELECT COUNT(*) as `count`, SUM(`hocphan`.`sotinchi`) as `sum` FROM `hocphan`, `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`, `caytientrinhsinhvien` WHERE `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`.`mahocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`.`idcaytientrinh` = `caytientrinhsinhvien`.`idcaytientrinh` AND `caytientrinhsinhvien`.`idsinhvien`='17004004' AND `hocphan`.`mahocphan` NOT IN(SELECT `diem`.`idhocphan` FROM `diem` WHERE `diem`.`idsinhvien`='17004004');
SELECT COUNT(*) as `count`, SUM(`hocphan`.`sotinchi`) as `sum` FROM `hocphan`, `diem` WHERE `diem`.`idhocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `diem`.`idsinhvien`='17004004';
SELECT COUNT(*) as `count`, SUM(`hocphan`.`sotinchi`) as `sum` FROM `hocphan`, `diem` WHERE `diem`.`idhocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `diem`.`diem` < 1 AND `diem`.`idsinhvien`='17004004';
SELECT `diem`, `hocphan`.`tenhocphan`, `hocphan`.`sotinchi` FROM `diem`, `hocphan` WHERE `diem`.`idhocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `diem`.`idsinhvien` = '17004004';
SELECT `hoten`,`taikhoan` FROM `taikhoan` WHERE `taikhoan`='17004004'

SELECT COUNT(*) as `count`, SUM(`hocphan`.`sotinchi`) as `sum` FROM `hocphan`, `diem` WHERE `diem`.`idhocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `diem`.`idsinhvien`='17004073';
SELECT COUNT(*) as `count`, SUM(`hocphan`.`sotinchi`) as `sum` FROM `hocphan`, `diem` WHERE `diem`.`idhocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `diem`.`diem` < 1 AND `diem`.`idsinhvien`='17004073';
SELECT `diem`, `hocphan`.`tenhocphan`, `hocphan`.`sotinchi` FROM `diem`, `hocphan` WHERE `diem`.`idhocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `diem`.`idsinhvien` = '17004073';

SELECT `hocphan`.`mahocphan`, `hocphan`.`tenhocphan`, `hocphan`.`sotinchi` FROM `hocphan`, `chunhiem`, `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`, `caytientrinhsinhvien` WHERE `caytientrinhsinhvien`.`idsinhvien` = `chunhiem`.`idsinhvien` AND `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`.`mahocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`.`idcaytientrinh` = `caytientrinhsinhvien`.`idcaytientrinh` AND `caytientrinhsinhvien`.`idsinhvien`='170040014' AND `chunhiem`.`idgiaovien`='giaovien1';
SELECT `diem` FROM `diem` WHERE `idhocphan`='CB1106' AND `idsinhvien`='170040014'

SELECT COUNT(*) as `count`, SUM(`hocphan`.`sotinchi`) as `sum` FROM `hocphan`, `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`, `caytientrinhsinhvien` WHERE `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`.`mahocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`.`idcaytientrinh` = `caytientrinhsinhvien`.`idcaytientrinh` AND `caytientrinhsinhvien`.`idsinhvien`='17004073' AND `hocphan`.`mahocphan` NOT IN(SELECT `diem`.`idhocphan` FROM `diem` WHERE `diem`.`idsinhvien`='17004073');

SELECT COUNT(*) as `count`, SUM(`hocphan`.`sotinchi`) as `sum` FROM `hocphan`, `diem` WHERE `diem`.`idhocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `diem`.`diem` < 1 AND `diem`.`idsinhvien`='17004073';
SELECT `diem`, `hocphan`.`tenhocphan`, `hocphan`.`sotinchi` FROM `diem`, `hocphan` WHERE `diem`.`idhocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `diem`.`idsinhvien` = '17004073';

SELECT taikhoan, hoten, tenloaitaikhoan, idloaitaikhoan FROM `taikhoan`, `loaitaikhoan` WHERE `taikhoan` = '17004004' AND `matkhau` = 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e' AND `idloaitaikhoan` = `loaitaikhoan`
SELECT * FROM `hocky`
SELECT `mahocphan`, `tenhocphan`, `sotinchi`, `hocphantienquyet` as mahocphantienquyet FROM `hocphan`;
SELECT DISTINCT `hocphan`.`mahocphan`, `hocphan`.`tenhocphan`, `hocphan`.`sotinchi` FROM `hocphan`, `dangkyhocphan`, `taikhoan` WHERE `dangkyhocphan`.`idhocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `dangkyhocphan`.`idsinhvien`='17004004' AND `dangkyhocphan`.`idhocky`='1';
SELECT taikhoan, hoten, tenloaitaikhoan, idloaitaikhoan FROM `taikhoan`, `loaitaikhoan` WHERE `taikhoan` = 'admin' AND `matkhau` = 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e' AND `idloaitaikhoan` = `loaitaikhoan`
SELECT `idcaytientrinh`, `tencaytientrinh`, `tenkhoa` FROM `caytientrinh` WHERE 1
SELECT `hocphan`.`mahocphan`, `tenhocphan`, `sotinchi` FROM `hocphan`, `hocphantrongcaytientrinh` WHERE `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`.`mahocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`.`idcaytientrinh`='5';
SELECT `mahocphan`, `tenhocphan`, `sotinchi` FROM `hocphan`;
SELECT `tencaytientrinh` FROM `caytientrinh` WHERE `idcaytientrinh`='5';
INSERT INTO `hocphantrongcaytientrinh` (`idcaytientrinh`, `mahocphan`) VALUES ('5', 'TH1326'),('5', 'TH1606'),('5', 'TH1607'),('5', 'TH1608')
SELECT `hocphan`.`mahocphan`, `tenhocphan`, `sotinchi` FROM `hocphan`, `hocphantrongcaytientrinh` WHERE `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`.`mahocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`.`idcaytientrinh`='5';
SELECT `mahocphan`, `tenhocphan`, `sotinchi` FROM `hocphan`;
SELECT `tencaytientrinh` FROM `caytientrinh` WHERE `idcaytientrinh`='5';
SELECT taikhoan, hoten, tenloaitaikhoan, idloaitaikhoan FROM `taikhoan`, `loaitaikhoan` WHERE `taikhoan` = '17004004' AND `matkhau` = 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e' AND `idloaitaikhoan` = `loaitaikhoan`
SELECT COUNT(*) as `count`, SUM(`hocphan`.`sotinchi`) as `sum` FROM `hocphan`, `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`, `caytientrinhsinhvien` WHERE `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`.`mahocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `hocphantrongcaytientrinh`.`idcaytientrinh` = `caytientrinhsinhvien`.`idcaytientrinh` AND `caytientrinhsinhvien`.`idsinhvien`='17004004' AND `hocphan`.`mahocphan` NOT IN(SELECT `diem`.`idhocphan` FROM `diem` WHERE `diem`.`idsinhvien`='17004004');

SELECT `idcaytientrinh`, `tencaytientrinh`, `tenkhoa` FROM `caytientrinh` WHERE 1
SELECT `sv`.`hoten` as `sinhvien`, `sv`.`taikhoan` as `idsinhvien` FROM `chunhiem`, `taikhoan` as `sv`, `taikhoan` as `gv` WHERE `chunhiem`.`idsinhvien` = `sv`.`taikhoan` AND `chunhiem`.`idgiaovien` = `gv`.`taikhoan` AND `gv`.`taikhoan`='giaovien1'

SELECT COUNT(*) as `count`, SUM(`hocphan`.`sotinchi`) as `sum` FROM `hocphan`, `diem` WHERE `diem`.`idhocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `diem`.`idsinhvien`='17004001';
SELECT COUNT(*) as `count`, SUM(`hocphan`.`sotinchi`) as `sum` FROM `hocphan`, `diem` WHERE `diem`.`idhocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `diem`.`diem` < 1 AND `diem`.`idsinhvien`='17004001';
SELECT `diem`, `hocphan`.`tenhocphan`, `hocphan`.`sotinchi` FROM `diem`, `hocphan` WHERE `diem`.`idhocphan` = `hocphan`.`mahocphan` AND `diem`.`idsinhvien` = '17004001';
